import React from 'react';
import {Container,Grid,Box} from '@mui/material';

function Header(props) {
    return (
        <React.Fragment>
      <Container maxWidth="sm">
      <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
      <Grid container spacing={2}>
        <Grid item xs={8}>
          <Item>xs=8</Item>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={4}>
          <Item>xs=4</Item>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={4}>
          <Item>xs=4</Item>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={8}>
          <Item>xs=8</Item>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
        </Container>
        </React.Fragment>
    );
}

export default Header;
